TO: PROF. JOHN KENNETH SIMON1

TL (XEROX), 1 p.





Montreux-Palace Hotel

Montreux, Switzerland

February 15, 1971

Dear Mr. Simon,

Many thanks for your reprint from Modern Language Notes, Vol. 83, No. 4, May, 1968, with the interesting item at the foot of page 546.

